-hover/img:bg-black/10 transition-colors duration-700"></div></div></div><div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 order-2 lg:order-1 pt-8 lg:pt-0"><div class="max-w-[500px] mx-auto text-center"><span class="font-body text-[13px] font-light uppercase tracking-eyebrow text-eyebrow mb-0 block uppercase">RELAX</span><h2 class="font-display text-[32px] md:text-[56px] md:leading-[56px] mt-4">AN OASIS OF TRANQUILITY</h2><p class="font-body text-[18px] leading-[32px] text-primary/80 mt-4">Enjoy the serene and blissful atmosphere of the Armani/SPA, offering unique treatments and exclusive services designed to help you fully unwind and regenerate.

